com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang

Class DeltaSet<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.DoubleBufferSet<K,Delta<K>>
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.DeltaSet<K>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type parameter

    public class DeltaSet<K>
extends DoubleBufferSet<K,Delta<K>>
    This is a collection of Deltas being staged for particular layers. Provides indexing capabilities to reference the deltas based on physical references (to double[] objects) and based on logical referants (i.e. layers) Provides collection-arithmetic operations appropriate to the Delta's vector geometric archtype.
